elements.name: As a first user I say hi to a second user

steps.name: I click on element having css selector "a#home-start-drawing-button"
I enter "Kraken1" into input field having id "nickName"
I select option with value "2" for dropdown with id "boardType"
I enter "Example Board" into input field having id "boardTitle"
I click on element having id "createBoardButton"
I store a variable with the current url
I send a signal to user 2 containing "hi"
